installation using TOMCAT-jenkins:-
====================================
Steps:-

  cd /opt
  5 wget http://mirrors.estointernet.in/apache/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.27/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.27.tar.gz
  6 ls
  7 tar -xvf apache-tomcat-9.0.27.tar.gz
  8 ls
  9 cd apache-tomcat-9.0.27
  10 cd webapps/
  11 ls
  12 wget http://mirrors.jenkins.io/war-stable/latest/jenkins.war
  13 cd â€¦/bin
  14 ls
  15 ./startup.sh

